data.description: Immaculate three year old home. This home offers an open feel through out the home. The open living space includes a spacious kitchen with large island, two pantries, quartz counter tops, plus a living room with a gas log fireplace and a dining room that accesses the rear patio. Wood like tile through out the living areas. Primary bedroom offers large walk in closet, shower and tub. Flex room just off of the master, makes a great office or children's playroom. An amazing over sized 3 car garage. The two car size is 28' deep. Yes the F150 extended bed will fit. Just up the street you will find the Splash pad, walking paths, Swimming Pool, Basketball courts, fitness center.
